.
Gaze not there, Howard,
said
she
; the
injuries of the mother are
past
redress
; but behold
your child, make reparation here!
Howard, the gay, the
thoughtless
,
dissipated
Howard
was
struck
to the heart. He
saw
the once lovely,
blooming, cheerful Mina, an inanimate
mass
.
Those
