,
who had neither rank or wealth to recommend her.
Rachel
saw
the
struggle
of his mind, and, attributing
that to pride which was only the effect of caution,
resolved
never to intrude
herself
into a family which would
look upon her connexion as degrading to its principal
branch.
Having therefore formed a plan for her future
conduct
,
Rachel took an affectionate leave of the worthy
Doctor and his
sister
, and a very cool one of Tabitha,
and departed in the
stage
-coach for London,
resolving
