shall
I tell her did her
the honour to call?
My name is Dudley,
said
Rachel.
Dudley! is it
possible
; the
sister
of my friend
Reuben
?
The
same
!
How happy I am,
Miss
Dudley! Give me leave
to wait on you to your place of
residence
. I
wish
to
ask
after your brother; I have
also
