?
said
the wretch who had pretended to detect her.
No,
said
the officer; I do not think
she
can be
guilty; or if
she
is, extreme
necessity
alone could have
driven her to
such
an expedient. How are you,
ma'am?
seeing
Rachel begin to revive.
She looked wildly round her, put her hand to her
head as though endeavouring to recollect why or how
