said
Spriggins.
I wonder what made her faint,
said
Belle.
Why lawk, Belle! replied the
sister
, you know
she
has always lived in the country, and
so
I
suppose
the lights, and the
noise
, and the heat
Just
then they arrived at home, and in a few
minutes
they were all
seated
round the
