You have an aunt, Hamden Auberry,
said
Rachel
with
firmness
, and on her depends your future
fortune. She will not approve of the untitled,
unportioned
Rachel for your wife.
Do not name her. I will renounce her favour.
I will henceforth live but for you.
Hamden,
said
Rachel, and her features
assumed
a
