Not entirely
so
.
What, I
suppose
your friends knew it?
I have no friends in England.
None?
No, not one. I have a brother, a dear,
respectable
,
worthy brother; but he is in America.
In America? Dear me; what all
amongst
the
blacks and the wild Indians?
Rachel could not
suppress
