some
circumstances
that I
understand
have taken place, and
knowing your extreme
sensibility
, cannot be
surprised
that they have injured both your health and peace of
mind. But where are you going now?
To America,
said
she
, in
pursuit
of my
husband
.
You are married, then,
said
I.
Yes,
she
replied, and fixing her eyes on my face,
did you not know it?
No, how
should
I? I have been in Ireland
these
two months
past
.
Just
then the
sailors
called to her
to get into the boat. She tendered me her hand.
God
bless
you, my good Doctor,
said
she
. I
shook
her hand, helped her in, and
And
she
is really gone, then, cried Hamden
frantickly.
The Doctor
raised
his eyes; the agitated
