Why does it affect me? Oh! Sir, I am the
husband
of Rachel! It is me
she
is gone in
pursuit
of.
I have
deserted
, abandoned,
forsaken
her; I thought
her depraved; I was told
Yes, and
so
have I been told,
said
the Doctor
with vehemence,
striking
